Title: Introducing Agent HQ: your mission control for AI agents
Description:
Meet Agent HQ, your new mission control for working with AI agents on GitHub. From a single view, you can see all agent sessions across your projects, assign new tasks, track progress, and review code. Plus, move seamlessly between the CLI, web, and your IDE, working wherever makes sense for you.
